<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Ʋba miko holitopa ƲIT145</title>
<time_sig>C.M. (8.6.8.6.)</time_sig>
<aka>&quot;Seek ye the Lord.&quot;</aka>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Ʋba miko holitopa
 Im ʋlla puta ma!
 Himonasi fehna kak o̱
 Wakayʋt ho mintí,

[V2]
 Ʋba Mi̱ko im ai a̱hli
 Ʋhleha puta ka
 Iba ta̱klʋt hikia hosh
 Taloho̱wa lashke.

[V3]
 Momʋt wakayʋt hikiʋt
 Oh aiokpahanchí;
 Himonasi fehna kak o̱
 Ʋba Mi̱ko hoyó.

[V4]
 Himak pilla nitak yukpa
 Ʋba nitak mak o̱,
 Nana chinto fehna mak osh
 Otʋna hi oke.

[V5]
 Kʋta hak osh ʋba Mi̱ko
 Iba nohowa chi̱?
 Hina malʋtha, achi ka
 Foyuka chi̱ hoh cho?

[V6]
 Himonasi fehna kak o̱,
 Shilombish ʋbi ya̱
 Il a mokoffit taiyahlit,
 Hʋsh i̱ hlakoffashke.

[V7]
 Ish a noho̱wa chi̱ hoka,
 Ʋba anumpa hʋt,
 Isht a holihtʋt taiyahʋt
 Chi afolublishke.</lyrics>
<author>Cyrus Kingsbury, Tune: &quot;Seek ye the Lord.&quot;</author>
<hymn_number>145</hymn_number>
</song>